{
  "video_id": "b9jb9UjCpik",
  "title": "Salvatore Iaconesi: What happened when I open-sourced my brain cancer",
  "json": [
    {
      "index": 1,
      "start_time": 14220.0,
      "end_time": 17315.0,
      "text": "This back here was my brain cancer."
    },
    {
      "index": 2,
      "start_time": 19125.0,
      "end_time": 20845.0,
      "text": "Isn&#39;t it nice?"
    },
    {
      "index": 3,
      "start_time": 20869.0,
      "end_time": 23312.0,
      "text": "(Laughter)"
    },
    {
      "index": 4,
      "start_time": 23336.0,
      "end_time": 25798.0,
      "text": "The key phrase is \"was,\""
    },
    {
      "index": 5,
      "start_time": 25822.0,
      "end_time": 27457.0,
      "text": "phew."
    },
    {
      "index": 6,
      "start_time": 27481.0,
      "end_time": 32523.0,
      "text": "(Applause)"
    },
    {
      "index": 7,
      "start_time": 32546.0,
      "end_time": 36714.0,
      "text": "Having brain cancer was really, as you can imagine,"
    },
    {
      "index": 8,
      "start_time": 36739.0,
      "end_time": 38590.0,
      "text": "shocking news for me."
    },
    {
      "index": 9,
      "start_time": 38615.0,
      "end_time": 40984.0,
      "text": "I knew nothing about cancer."
    },
    {
      "index": 10,
      "start_time": 42590.0,
      "end_time": 45870.0,
      "text": "In Western cultures, when you have cancer,"
    },
    {
      "index": 11,
      "start_time": 45894.0,
      "end_time": 48102.0,
      "text": "it&#39;s as if you disappear in a way."
    },
    {
      "index": 12,
      "start_time": 48509.0,
      "end_time": 55123.0,
      "text": "Your life as a complex human being is replaced by medical data:"
    },
    {
      "index": 13,
      "start_time": 55147.0,
      "end_time": 61233.0,
      "text": "Your images, your exams, your lab values,"
    },
    {
      "index": 14,
      "start_time": 61258.0,
      "end_time": 62933.0,
      "text": "a list of medicines."
    },
    {
      "index": 15,
      "start_time": 63740.0,
      "end_time": 65734.0,
      "text": "And everyone changes as well."
    },
    {
      "index": 16,
      "start_time": 66439.0,
      "end_time": 68794.0,
      "text": "You suddenly become a disease on legs."
    },
    {
      "index": 17,
      "start_time": 69384.0,
      "end_time": 73488.0,
      "text": "Doctors start speaking a language which you don&#39;t understand."
    },
    {
      "index": 18,
      "start_time": 73983.0,
      "end_time": 79313.0,
      "text": "They start pointing their fingers"
    },
    {
      "index": 19,
      "start_time": 79337.0,
      "end_time": 83484.0,
      "text": "at your body and your images."
    },
    {
      "index": 20,
      "start_time": 84187.0,
      "end_time": 87210.0,
      "text": "People start changing as well"
    },
    {
      "index": 21,
      "start_time": 87234.0,
      "end_time": 91760.0,
      "text": "because they start dealing with the disease,"
    },
    {
      "index": 22,
      "start_time": 91100.0,
      "end_time": 93434.0,
      "text": "instead of with the human being."
    },
    {
      "index": 23,
      "start_time": 93459.0,
      "end_time": 95620.0,
      "text": "They say, \"What did the doctor say?\""
    },
    {
      "index": 24,
      "start_time": 95644.0,
      "end_time": 98480.0,
      "text": "before even saying, \"Hello.\""
    },
    {
      "index": 25,
      "start_time": 99976.0,
      "end_time": 101899.0,
      "text": "And in the meanwhile,"
    },
    {
      "index": 26,
      "start_time": 101923.0,
      "end_time": 107890.0,
      "text": "you&#39;re left with questions to which nobody gives an answer."
    },
    {
      "index": 27,
      "start_time": 107113.0,
      "end_time": 109864.0,
      "text": "These are the \"Can I?\" questions:"
    },
    {
      "index": 28,
      "start_time": 109888.0,
      "end_time": 111883.0,
      "text": "Can I work while I have cancer?"
    },
    {
      "index": 29,
      "start_time": 112507.0,
      "end_time": 117540.0,
      "text": "Can I study? Can I make love? Can I be creative?"
    },
    {
      "index": 30,
      "start_time": 117864.0,
      "end_time": 121318.0,
      "text": "And you wonder, \"What have I done to deserve this?\""
    },
    {
      "index": 31,
      "start_time": 121342.0,
      "end_time": 125476.0,
      "text": "You wonder, \"Can I change something about my lifestyle?\""
    },
    {
      "index": 32,
      "start_time": 125500.0,
      "end_time": 128174.0,
      "text": "You wonder, \"Can I do something?"
    },
    {
      "index": 33,
      "start_time": 128198.00000000001,
      "end_time": 130293.00000000001,
      "text": "Are there any other options?\""
    },
    {
      "index": 34,
      "start_time": 132333.0,
      "end_time": 137964.0,
      "text": "And, obviously, doctors are the good guys in all these scenarios,"
    },
    {
      "index": 35,
      "start_time": 137988.0,
      "end_time": 143910.0,
      "text": "because they are very professional and dedicated to curing you."
    },
    {
      "index": 36,
      "start_time": 143934.0,
      "end_time": 149168.0,
      "text": "But they also are very used to having to deal with patients,"
    },
    {
      "index": 37,
      "start_time": 149192.0,
      "end_time": 156124.0,
      "text": "so I&#39;d say that they sometimes lose the idea that this is torture for you"
    },
    {
      "index": 38,
      "start_time": 156148.0,
      "end_time": 161790.0,
      "text": "and that you become, literally, a patient --"
    },
    {
      "index": 39,
      "start_time": 161103.0,
      "end_time": 163514.0,
      "text": "\"patient\" means \"the one who waits.\""
    },
    {
      "index": 40,
      "start_time": 163538.0,
      "end_time": 164931.0,
      "text": "(Laughter)"
    },
    {
      "index": 41,
      "start_time": 164955.0,
      "end_time": 169144.0,
      "text": "Things are changing, but classically,"
    },
    {
      "index": 42,
      "start_time": 169168.0,
      "end_time": 174817.0,
      "text": "they tend to not engage you in any way to learn about your condition,"
    },
    {
      "index": 43,
      "start_time": 174841.0,
      "end_time": 178964.0,
      "text": "to get your friends and family engaged,"
    },
    {
      "index": 44,
      "start_time": 178988.0,
      "end_time": 182728.0,
      "text": "or showing you ways in which you can change your lifestyle"
    },
    {
      "index": 45,
      "start_time": 182752.0,
      "end_time": 185142.0,
      "text": "to minimize the risks of what you&#39;re going through."
    },
    {
      "index": 46,
      "start_time": 186830.0,
      "end_time": 189947.0,
      "text": "But instead, you&#39;re forced there to wait"
    },
    {
      "index": 47,
      "start_time": 189971.0,
      "end_time": 194992.0,
      "text": "in the hands of a series of very professional strangers."
    },
    {
      "index": 48,
      "start_time": 196815.0,
      "end_time": 198890.0,
      "text": "While I was in the hospital,"
    },
    {
      "index": 49,
      "start_time": 198914.0,
      "end_time": 202332.0,
      "text": "I asked for a printed-out picture of my cancer"
    },
    {
      "index": 50,
      "start_time": 202356.0,
      "end_time": 204415.0,
      "text": "and I spoke with it."
    },
    {
      "index": 51,
      "start_time": 205120.0,
      "end_time": 207318.0,
      "text": "It was really hard to obtain,"
    },
    {
      "index": 52,
      "start_time": 207342.0,
      "end_time": 212270.0,
      "text": "because it&#39;s not common practice to ask for a picture of your own cancer."
    },
    {
      "index": 53,
      "start_time": 212294.0,
      "end_time": 214590.0,
      "text": "I talked to it and I said,"
    },
    {
      "index": 54,
      "start_time": 214830.0,
      "end_time": 218611.0,
      "text": "\"Okay, cancer, you&#39;re not all there is to me."
    },
    {
      "index": 55,
      "start_time": 218635.0,
      "end_time": 220623.0,
      "text": "There&#39;s more to me."
    },
    {
      "index": 56,
      "start_time": 220647.0,
      "end_time": 227610.0,
      "text": "A cure, whichever it is, will have to deal with the whole of me.\""
    },
    {
      "index": 57,
      "start_time": 227860.0,
      "end_time": 233000.0,
      "text": "And so, the next day, I left the hospital against medical advice."
    },
    {
      "index": 58,
      "start_time": 233240.0,
      "end_time": 237592.0,
      "text": "I was determined to change my relationship with the cancer"
    },
    {
      "index": 59,
      "start_time": 237616.0,
      "end_time": 240460.0,
      "text": "and I was determined to learn more about my cancer"
    },
    {
      "index": 60,
      "start_time": 240484.0,
      "end_time": 244530.0,
      "text": "before doing anything as drastic as a surgery."
    },
    {
      "index": 61,
      "start_time": 246370.0,
      "end_time": 252927.0,
      "text": "I&#39;m an artist, I use several forms of open-source technologies"
    },
    {
      "index": 62,
      "start_time": 252951.0,
      "end_time": 255470.0,
      "text": "and open information in my practice."
    },
    {
      "index": 63,
      "start_time": 255494.0,
      "end_time": 261581.0,
      "text": "So my best bet was to get it all out there, get the information out there,"
    },
    {
      "index": 64,
      "start_time": 261605.00000000003,
      "end_time": 267192.0,
      "text": "and use it so that it could be accessed by anyone."
    },
    {
      "index": 65,
      "start_time": 268269.0,
      "end_time": 272222.0,
      "text": "So I created a website, which is called La Cura,"
    },
    {
      "index": 66,
      "start_time": 272246.0,
      "end_time": 275373.0,
      "text": "on which I put my medical data, online."
    },
    {
      "index": 67,
      "start_time": 275398.0,
      "end_time": 277271.0,
      "text": "I actually had to hack it"
    },
    {
      "index": 68,
      "start_time": 277295.0,
      "end_time": 281451.0,
      "text": "and that&#39;s a thing which we can talk about in another speech."
    },
    {
      "index": 69,
      "start_time": 281475.0,
      "end_time": 282798.0,
      "text": "(Laughter)"
    },
    {
      "index": 70,
      "start_time": 282822.0,
      "end_time": 285379.0,
      "text": "I chose this word, La Cura --"
    },
    {
      "index": 71,
      "start_time": 285403.0,
      "end_time": 287738.0,
      "text": "La Cura in Italian means \"the cure\" --"
    },
    {
      "index": 72,
      "start_time": 287762.0,
      "end_time": 290490.0,
      "text": "because in many different cultures,"
    },
    {
      "index": 73,
      "start_time": 290514.0,
      "end_time": 294621.0,
      "text": "the word \"cure\" can mean many different things."
    },
    {
      "index": 74,
      "start_time": 295660.0,
      "end_time": 296724.0,
      "text": "In our Western cultures,"
    },
    {
      "index": 75,
      "start_time": 296749.0,
      "end_time": 301218.0,
      "text": "it means eradicating or reversing a disease,"
    },
    {
      "index": 76,
      "start_time": 301242.0,
      "end_time": 302746.0,
      "text": "but in different cultures,"
    },
    {
      "index": 77,
      "start_time": 302770.0,
      "end_time": 306325.0,
      "text": "for example, a culture from Asia,"
    },
    {
      "index": 78,
      "start_time": 306350.0,
      "end_time": 310462.0,
      "text": "from the Mediterranean, from Latin countries, from Africa,"
    },
    {
      "index": 79,
      "start_time": 310486.0,
      "end_time": 312209.0,
      "text": "it can mean many more things."
    },
    {
      "index": 80,
      "start_time": 312628.0,
      "end_time": 317991.0,
      "text": "Of course, I was interested in the opinions of doctors"
    },
    {
      "index": 81,
      "start_time": 318150.0,
      "end_time": 320240.0,
      "text": "and healthcare providers,"
    },
    {
      "index": 82,
      "start_time": 320264.0,
      "end_time": 326235.0,
      "text": "but I was also interested in the cure of the artist, of the poet,"
    },
    {
      "index": 83,
      "start_time": 326259.0,
      "end_time": 328412.0,
      "text": "of the designer,"
    },
    {
      "index": 84,
      "start_time": 328436.0,
      "end_time": 332356.0,
      "text": "of, who knows, the musicians."
    },
    {
      "index": 85,
      "start_time": 332889.0,
      "end_time": 335765.0,
      "text": "I was interested in the social cure,"
    },
    {
      "index": 86,
      "start_time": 335789.0,
      "end_time": 338462.0,
      "text": "I was interested in the psychological cure,"
    },
    {
      "index": 87,
      "start_time": 338487.0,
      "end_time": 340977.0,
      "text": "I was interested in the spiritual cure,"
    },
    {
      "index": 88,
      "start_time": 341100.0,
      "end_time": 344340.0,
      "text": "I was interested in the emotional cure,"
    },
    {
      "index": 89,
      "start_time": 344590.0,
      "end_time": 346857.0,
      "text": "I was interested in any form of cure."
    },
    {
      "index": 90,
      "start_time": 348920.0,
      "end_time": 352592.0,
      "text": "And, it worked."
    },
    {
      "index": 91,
      "start_time": 352616.0,
      "end_time": 355945.0,
      "text": "The La Cura website went viral."
    },
    {
      "index": 92,
      "start_time": 355969.0,
      "end_time": 360670.0,
      "text": "I received lots of media attention from Italy and from abroad"
    },
    {
      "index": 93,
      "start_time": 360694.0,
      "end_time": 366416.0,
      "text": "and I quickly received more than 500,000 contacts --"
    },
    {
      "index": 94,
      "start_time": 366440.0,
      "end_time": 368354.0,
      "text": "emails, social networking --"
    },
    {
      "index": 95,
      "start_time": 368378.0,
      "end_time": 371549.0,
      "text": "most of them were a suggestion on how to cure my cancer,"
    },
    {
      "index": 96,
      "start_time": 371573.0,
      "end_time": 374979.0,
      "text": "but more of them were about how to cure myself"
    },
    {
      "index": 97,
      "start_time": 375400.0,
      "end_time": 377319.0,
      "text": "as a full individual."
    },
    {
      "index": 98,
      "start_time": 378283.0,
      "end_time": 382341.0,
      "text": "For example, many thousands of videos,"
    },
    {
      "index": 99,
      "start_time": 382365.0,
      "end_time": 386295.0,
      "text": "images, pictures, art performances"
    },
    {
      "index": 100,
      "start_time": 386319.0,
      "end_time": 388800.0,
      "text": "were produced for La Cura."
    },
    {
      "index": 101,
      "start_time": 388756.0,
      "end_time": 392300.0,
      "text": "For example, here we see Francesca Fini in her performance."
    },
    {
      "index": 102,
      "start_time": 393141.0,
      "end_time": 397498.0,
      "text": "Or, as artist Patrick Lichty has done:"
    },
    {
      "index": 103,
      "start_time": 397522.0,
      "end_time": 402750.0,
      "text": "He produced a 3D sculpture of my tumor"
    },
    {
      "index": 104,
      "start_time": 402100.0,
      "end_time": 404797.0,
      "text": "and put it on sale on Thingiverse."
    },
    {
      "index": 105,
      "start_time": 404821.0,
      "end_time": 407200.0,
      "text": "Now you can have my cancer, too!"
    },
    {
      "index": 106,
      "start_time": 407440.0,
      "end_time": 409556.0,
      "text": "(Laughter)"
    },
    {
      "index": 107,
      "start_time": 409581.0,
      "end_time": 412974.0,
      "text": "Which is a nice thing, if you think about it,"
    },
    {
      "index": 108,
      "start_time": 412998.0,
      "end_time": 414782.0,
      "text": "we can share our cancer."
    },
    {
      "index": 109,
      "start_time": 416234.0,
      "end_time": 418609.0,
      "text": "And this was going on --"
    },
    {
      "index": 110,
      "start_time": 418633.0,
      "end_time": 421994.0,
      "text": "scientists, the traditional medicine experts,"
    },
    {
      "index": 111,
      "start_time": 422180.0,
      "end_time": 423681.0,
      "text": "several researchers, doctors --"
    },
    {
      "index": 112,
      "start_time": 423705.0,
      "end_time": 426377.0,
      "text": "all connected with me to give advice."
    },
    {
      "index": 113,
      "start_time": 426401.0,
      "end_time": 428296.0,
      "text": "With all this information and support,"
    },
    {
      "index": 114,
      "start_time": 428320.0,
      "end_time": 433985.0,
      "text": "I was able to form a team of several neurosurgeons,"
    },
    {
      "index": 115,
      "start_time": 434900.0,
      "end_time": 436971.0,
      "text": "traditional doctors,"
    },
    {
      "index": 116,
      "start_time": 436995.0,
      "end_time": 443120.0,
      "text": "oncologists, and several hundred volunteers"
    },
    {
      "index": 117,
      "start_time": 443144.0,
      "end_time": 446349.0,
      "text": "with whom I was able to discuss"
    },
    {
      "index": 118,
      "start_time": 446373.0,
      "end_time": 451772.0,
      "text": "the information I was receiving, which is very important."
    },
    {
      "index": 119,
      "start_time": 451796.0,
      "end_time": 458141.0,
      "text": "And together, we were able to form a strategy for my own cure"
    },
    {
      "index": 120,
      "start_time": 458165.0,
      "end_time": 461792.0,
      "text": "in many languages, according to many cultures."
    },
    {
      "index": 121,
      "start_time": 461816.0,
      "end_time": 464981.0,
      "text": "And the current strategy spans the whole world"
    },
    {
      "index": 122,
      "start_time": 465500.0,
      "end_time": 467603.0,
      "text": "and thousands of years of human history,"
    },
    {
      "index": 123,
      "start_time": 467627.0,
      "end_time": 469686.0,
      "text": "which is quite remarkable for me."
    },
    {
      "index": 124,
      "start_time": 469710.0,
      "end_time": 471370.0,
      "text": "[Surgery]"
    },
    {
      "index": 125,
      "start_time": 471394.0,
      "end_time": 476323.0,
      "text": "The follow-up MRIs showed, luckily, little to no growth of the cancer."
    },
    {
      "index": 126,
      "start_time": 477500.0,
      "end_time": 480402.0,
      "text": "So I was able to take my time and choose."
    },
    {
      "index": 127,
      "start_time": 480426.0,
      "end_time": 484670.0,
      "text": "I chose the doctor I wanted to work with,"
    },
    {
      "index": 128,
      "start_time": 484910.0,
      "end_time": 486465.0,
      "text": "I chose the hospital I wanted to stay in,"
    },
    {
      "index": 129,
      "start_time": 486489.0,
      "end_time": 490476.0,
      "text": "and in the meanwhile, I was supported by thousands of people,"
    },
    {
      "index": 130,
      "start_time": 490500.0,
      "end_time": 493727.0,
      "text": "none of whom felt pity for me."
    },
    {
      "index": 131,
      "start_time": 493751.0,
      "end_time": 499405.0,
      "text": "Everyone felt like they could take an active role"
    },
    {
      "index": 132,
      "start_time": 499429.0,
      "end_time": 501241.0,
      "text": "in helping me to get well,"
    },
    {
      "index": 133,
      "start_time": 501265.0,
      "end_time": 504630.0,
      "text": "and this was the most important part of La Cura."
    },
    {
      "index": 134,
      "start_time": 506810.0,
      "end_time": 507283.0,
      "text": "What are the outcomes?"
    },
    {
      "index": 135,
      "start_time": 508122.0,
      "end_time": 510455.0,
      "text": "I&#39;m fine, as you can see, pretty fine."
    },
    {
      "index": 136,
      "start_time": 510479.0,
      "end_time": 515770.0,
      "text": "(Applause)"
    },
    {
      "index": 137,
      "start_time": 515794.0,
      "end_time": 518203.0,
      "text": "I had excellent news"
    },
    {
      "index": 138,
      "start_time": 518227.0,
      "end_time": 519832.0,
      "text": "after the surgery --"
    },
    {
      "index": 139,
      "start_time": 519857.0,
      "end_time": 525352.0,
      "text": "I have -- I had a very low-grade glioma,"
    },
    {
      "index": 140,
      "start_time": 525376.0,
      "end_time": 529798.0,
      "text": "which is a \"good\" kind of cancer which doesn&#39;t grow a lot."
    },
    {
      "index": 141,
      "start_time": 529822.0,
      "end_time": 533275.0,
      "text": "I have completely changed my life and my lifestyle."
    },
    {
      "index": 142,
      "start_time": 534250.0,
      "end_time": 539375.0,
      "text": "Everything I did was thoughtfully designed to get me engaged."
    },
    {
      "index": 143,
      "start_time": 540550.0,
      "end_time": 544170.0,
      "text": "Up until the very last few minutes of the surgery,"
    },
    {
      "index": 144,
      "start_time": 544195.0,
      "end_time": 546162.0,
      "text": "which was very intense,"
    },
    {
      "index": 145,
      "start_time": 546186.0,
      "end_time": 550107.0,
      "text": "a matrix of electrodes was implanted in my brain"
    },
    {
      "index": 146,
      "start_time": 550131.0,
      "end_time": 551997.0,
      "text": "from this side,"
    },
    {
      "index": 147,
      "start_time": 552210.0,
      "end_time": 557253.0,
      "text": "to be able to build a functional map of what the brain controls."
    },
    {
      "index": 148,
      "start_time": 557278.0,
      "end_time": 560952.0,
      "text": "And right before the operation,"
    },
    {
      "index": 149,
      "start_time": 560976.0,
      "end_time": 567753.0,
      "text": "we were able to discuss the functional map of my brain"
    },
    {
      "index": 150,
      "start_time": 567777.0,
      "end_time": 572660.0,
      "text": "with the doctor, to understand which risks I was running into"
    },
    {
      "index": 151,
      "start_time": 572684.0,
      "end_time": 576288.0,
      "text": "and if there were any I wanted to avoid."
    },
    {
      "index": 152,
      "start_time": 576312.0,
      "end_time": 578428.0,
      "text": "Obviously, there were."
    },
    {
      "index": 153,
      "start_time": 578452.0,
      "end_time": 579505.0,
      "text": "[Open]"
    },
    {
      "index": 154,
      "start_time": 579529.0,
      "end_time": 584956.0,
      "text": "And this openness was really the fundamental part of La Cura."
    },
    {
      "index": 155,
      "start_time": 584980.0,
      "end_time": 589775.0,
      "text": "Thousands of people shared their stories, their experiences."
    },
    {
      "index": 156,
      "start_time": 589799.0,
      "end_time": 594403.0,
      "text": "Doctors got to talk with people they don&#39;t usually consult"
    },
    {
      "index": 157,
      "start_time": 594427.0,
      "end_time": 599346.0,
      "text": "when they think about cancer."
    },
    {
      "index": 158,
      "start_time": 599370.0,
      "end_time": 604190.0,
      "text": "I&#39;m a self-founding, continuous state of translation"
    },
    {
      "index": 159,
      "start_time": 604430.0,
      "end_time": 606339.0,
      "text": "among many different languages,"
    },
    {
      "index": 160,
      "start_time": 606363.0,
      "end_time": 610236.0,
      "text": "in which science meets emotion"
    },
    {
      "index": 161,
      "start_time": 610260.0,
      "end_time": 614896.0,
      "text": "and conventional research meets traditional research."
    },
    {
      "index": 162,
      "start_time": 614921.0,
      "end_time": 616239.0,
      "text": "[Society]"
    },
    {
      "index": 163,
      "start_time": 616263.0,
      "end_time": 621610.0,
      "text": "The most important thing of La Cura"
    },
    {
      "index": 164,
      "start_time": 621635.0,
      "end_time": 628635.0,
      "text": "was to feel like a part of a really engaged and connected society"
    },
    {
      "index": 165,
      "start_time": 628660.0,
      "end_time": 634780.0,
      "text": "whose wellness really depends on the wellness of all of its components."
    },
    {
      "index": 166,
      "start_time": 636253.0,
      "end_time": 640853.0,
      "text": "This global performance is my open-source cure for cancer."
    },
    {
      "index": 167,
      "start_time": 641873.0,
      "end_time": 643655.0,
      "text": "And from what I feel,"
    },
    {
      "index": 168,
      "start_time": 643679.0,
      "end_time": 646550.0,
      "text": "it&#39;s a cure for me, but for us all."
    },
    {
      "index": 169,
      "start_time": 646790.0,
      "end_time": 647232.0,
      "text": "Thank you."
    },
    {
      "index": 170,
      "start_time": 647256.0,
      "end_time": 649930.0,
      "text": "(Applause)."
    }
  ]
}